    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "On September 17, 1963, Mr. [REDACTED], an FBI agent of the Newport",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "News, Va. contingent, visited me at my place of employment (Ft. Eustis, Va.)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "to interview me as to my interest in the subject of unidentified flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "objects (UFO's). I understand that Mr. [REDACTED] prepared a formal report of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "that interview.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Since President Nixon recently has expressed his intention to assure that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "the privacy and civil liberties of individual citizens receive the protection",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "they deserve under our form of government, it is in the spirit of that assurance",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "that I respectfully request that you send me a copy of Mr. [REDACTED] report along",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "with a copy of all other documents in your files pertaining to my activities in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "the UFO-research field.",
      "status": "image_matched"
